#hm-note[
  Month 6 closes Quarter II. At this stage, the Tarot is no longer a study
  subject — it is a working instrument. A student who is still primarily doing
  keyword review or basic card-meaning study has not advanced their Tarot practice
  beyond Year One level. If this is the case, do not proceed without a direct
  conversation about why the practice has not deepened. The Tarot journal is the
  diagnostic: if it is thin, the practice is thin. If it is rich with genuine
  encounter, the practice is genuine.
]

