= ⬡ QUARTER II GATHERING — The Philosophic Sulphur of Metals

*Theme:* Alchemical almanacs compared; Adept-level Tarot spreads conducted as group practice.

#hm-note[
  The group Tarot reading at this gathering should use the personal alchemical
  spread format: each student lays their own spread simultaneously, then the
  group reads the positions in unison — first the card at "current state of the
  Work," then "what is blocking," then "what is opening." Reading these positions
  across all students at once often reveals collective themes in the cohort's
  experience of the Work at this stage.
]

*Students share:*
- Their personal alchemical mineral almanac for the coming year.
- Their personal alchemical spread: the layout and what it revealed about the
  current state and next operation.
- Progress on the Via Humida mineral work.
- Any experiences with the metal meditations from Year Two continued into Year Three.

